description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss St. Louis county ending the mask mandate, controversy surrounding “republican” candidates Jessie Sullivan & Alex Stovall, and the father-son duo arrested for starting a wildfire in California that misplaced & injured thousands of people.
